<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/394> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #394" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 4.35.1; Diod. 12.81.1; Chr. 354 (Arretino et Mevulliano); Degrassi 96, 374f. Under these Veii was granted a truce for twenty years, and the Aequi one for three (Liv. 4.35.2)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/393> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #393" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Omission of Horatius' name by Diod. leads Mommsen (RF 2.228) and Münzer (RE) to conclude that his name is not authentic. On Furius' filiation, see Fast. Cap. on 405. For Quinctius Diodorus has {Gr}." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertion/488> rdfs:label "Post Assertion: #488" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertion ;
